Summary: I just got out of my car and happen to look up and seen a white streak of light shoot across the sky
divs: sighting detailsi just got home from work at 6 pm pst and as i got out of my car i looked up i see this beam of white light - ascending upward at an angle with a blue center.. and it shot acrosed the sky\horizon in a flash towards the pacific. i never seen an object move that fast and no visual after that. i have lived by the airport for years since i was a kid and know that was no airplane, jet or helicopter. did anyone else report this? thanks, ryan
